[SPEAKER_00] jedna žena

636
00:43:04,179 --> 00:43:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] koja predstavlja Boži narod,

637
00:43:05,800 --> 00:43:07,980
[SPEAKER_00] Božijom snagom

638
00:43:07,980 --> 00:43:10,239
[SPEAKER_00] oslobađa se tih neprijatelja,

639
00:43:10,239 --> 00:43:12,739
[SPEAKER_00] to je u doba Marka Marulića,

640
00:43:12,739 --> 00:43:13,900
[SPEAKER_00] on piše u Juditi,

641
00:43:13,900 --> 00:43:14,820
[SPEAKER_00] ali je očito

642
00:43:14,820 --> 00:43:15,519
[SPEAKER_00] da misli

643
00:43:15,519 --> 00:43:16,460
[SPEAKER_00] na situaciju

644
00:43:16,460 --> 00:43:17,360
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj sad živi

645
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:18,519
[SPEAKER_00] i na trpljenje

646
00:43:18,519 --> 00:43:19,300
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatskog naroda

647
00:43:19,300 --> 00:43:20,960
[SPEAKER_00] pred osmanlijskim napadima

648
00:43:20,960 --> 00:43:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji su trajali

649
00:43:21,739 --> 00:43:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] i trajali,

650
00:43:22,380 --> 00:43:23,960
[SPEAKER_00] što je poznato

651
00:43:23,960 --> 00:43:24,719
[SPEAKER_00] iz njegove druge

652
00:43:24,719 --> 00:43:26,260
[SPEAKER_00] molitve suprotive Turkom,

653
00:43:26,340 --> 00:43:27,519
[SPEAKER_00] i angažmana,

654
00:43:27,519 --> 00:43:28,260
[SPEAKER_00] da koliko može

655
00:43:28,260 --> 00:43:29,219
[SPEAKER_00] i on se

656
00:43:29,219 --> 00:43:31,099
[SPEAKER_00] izravno uključiva u to,

657
00:43:31,099 --> 00:43:32,920
[SPEAKER_00] da koliko je moguće

658
00:43:32,920 --> 00:43:34,260
[SPEAKER_00] da se Hrvatskom narodu

659
00:43:34,260 --> 00:43:34,920
[SPEAKER_00] pomogne,

660
00:43:34,920 --> 00:43:35,760
[SPEAKER_00] jer Hrvatski narod

661
00:43:35,760 --> 00:43:36,840
[SPEAKER_00] zapravo tu stoji,

662
00:43:36,840 --> 00:43:37,059
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

663
00:43:37,059 --> 00:43:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] kao predziđe kršćanstva,

664
00:43:38,420 --> 00:43:38,659
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

665
00:43:38,659 --> 00:43:39,599
[SPEAKER_00] svi nekako

666
00:43:39,599 --> 00:43:40,739
[SPEAKER_00] uživaju zaštitu,

667
00:43:40,739 --> 00:43:41,059
[SPEAKER_00] evo,

668
00:43:41,059 --> 00:43:43,039
[SPEAKER_00] tako je to naša povijest

669
00:43:43,039 --> 00:43:43,639
[SPEAKER_00] i kažem,

670
00:43:43,719 --> 00:43:44,360
[SPEAKER_00] zato je Judita

671
00:43:44,360 --> 00:43:45,340
[SPEAKER_00] svojevrstna paradigma,

672
00:43:45,340 --> 00:43:46,780
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije Judita ono,

673
00:43:46,780 --> 00:43:47,079
[SPEAKER_00] e,

674
00:43:47,079 --> 00:43:48,880
[SPEAKER_00] to sam ti joj reći,

675
00:43:48,880 --> 00:43:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] kod Judite

676
00:43:50,079 --> 00:43:51,719
[SPEAKER_00] Bog više nije ratnik,

677
00:43:51,719 --> 00:43:52,739
[SPEAKER_00] što je možda prije

678
00:43:52,739 --> 00:43:53,960
[SPEAKER_00] u starom zavijetu

679
00:43:53,960 --> 00:43:55,440
[SPEAKER_00] bilo rat,

680
00:43:55,440 --> 00:43:56,000
[SPEAKER_00] voditi rat,

681
00:43:56,000 --> 00:43:56,320
[SPEAKER_00] ne, ne,

682
00:43:56,320 --> 00:43:58,219
[SPEAKER_00] kod Judite je vrlo specifična,

683
00:43:58,219 --> 00:43:59,280
[SPEAKER_00] jako draga,

684
00:43:59,280 --> 00:44:00,440
[SPEAKER_00] prekrasna slika,

685
00:44:00,440 --> 00:44:02,099
[SPEAKER_00] jedinstvena slika o Bogu,

686
00:44:02,099 --> 00:44:03,679
[SPEAKER_00] na dva mjesta se pojavlja.

687
00:44:03,679 --> 00:44:04,280
[SPEAKER_00] Od ko je Bog?

688
00:44:04,280 --> 00:44:06,699
[SPEAKER_00] Bog je onaj koji mrvi ratove.

689
00:44:06,699 --> 00:44:08,840
[SPEAKER_00] To nam pomaže prvo da shvatimo

690
00:44:08,840 --> 00:44:09,219
[SPEAKER_00] ta knjiga,

691
00:44:09,219 --> 00:44:10,380
[SPEAKER_00] uopće ni militaristička,

692
00:44:10,380 --> 00:44:11,639
[SPEAKER_00] niti pozivne ratovanje,

693
00:44:11,780 --> 00:44:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] prema da prvi dojem može biti.

694
00:44:13,599 --> 00:44:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] I drugo,

695
00:44:15,079 --> 00:44:16,920
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo da,

696
00:44:16,920 --> 00:44:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] nažalost,

697
00:44:17,380 --> 00:44:18,159
[SPEAKER_00] ratova ima,

698
00:44:18,159 --> 00:44:20,099
[SPEAKER_00] a Bog je onaj koji može riješiti

699
00:44:20,099 --> 00:44:21,179
[SPEAKER_00] onda i kad mi ne možemo.

700
00:44:21,179 --> 00:44:22,900
[SPEAKER_00] Mi često smo ljudi takvi da

701
00:44:22,900 --> 00:44:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] se zapetljamo

702
00:44:24,820 --> 00:44:25,679
[SPEAKER_00] i onda ratujemo,

703
00:44:25,679 --> 00:44:27,099
[SPEAKER_00] da zapravo ne znamo zašto ratujemo.

704
00:44:27,099 --> 00:44:27,300
[SPEAKER_00] Evo,

705
00:44:27,300 --> 00:44:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] Bog to može riješiti,

706
00:44:28,360 --> 00:44:29,619
[SPEAKER_00] ali to se tiče i naših

707
00:44:29,619 --> 00:44:31,619
[SPEAKER_00] običnih sukoba,

708
00:44:31,619 --> 00:44:32,699
[SPEAKER_00] međuljudskih,

709
00:44:32,699 --> 00:44:33,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji, hvala Bogu,

710
00:44:33,340 --> 00:44:35,000
[SPEAKER_00] nisu međunarodni rati.

711
00:44:35,000 --> 00:44:36,179
[SPEAKER_00] Kada smo mi u ratu,

712
00:44:36,179 --> 00:44:37,380
[SPEAKER_00] u obitelji,

713
00:44:37,380 --> 00:44:39,320
[SPEAKER_00] među kolega na prijateljima,

714
00:44:40,059 --> 00:44:41,659
[SPEAKER_00] njezina slika o Bogu je,

715
00:44:41,659 --> 00:44:43,159
[SPEAKER_00] dragi Bog,

716
00:44:43,159 --> 00:44:44,719
[SPEAKER_00] to može pretvoriti u prah,

717
00:44:44,719 --> 00:44:45,460
[SPEAKER_00] u mrvice.

718
00:44:45,460 --> 00:44:47,219
[SPEAKER_00] I onda kada nama to nije moguće.

719
00:44:47,219 --> 00:44:47,360
[SPEAKER_00] Evo,

720
00:44:47,360 --> 00:44:49,599
[SPEAKER_00] to je bitna promjena

721
00:44:49,599 --> 00:44:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] unutra staroga zavijeta.

722
00:44:51,559 --> 00:44:52,579
[SPEAKER_00] E,

723
00:44:52,579 --> 00:44:53,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali svakako,

724
00:44:53,420 --> 00:44:54,360
[SPEAKER_00] tu se svi slažu.

725
00:44:54,360 --> 00:44:56,679
[SPEAKER_00] Kako treba početi čita stari zavijet?

726
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:59,179
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da uzmete knjigu mudrosti.

727
00:44:59,179 --> 00:45:00,280
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je,

728
00:45:00,280 --> 00:45:01,500
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno,

729
00:45:01,500 --> 00:45:02,800
[SPEAKER_00] ona je sada smještena

730
00:45:02,800 --> 00:45:04,739
[SPEAKER_00] u sredinu staroga zavijeta,

731
00:45:04,739 --> 00:45:05,800
[SPEAKER_00] među mudrosne knjige.

732
00:45:05,800 --> 00:45:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ona je de facto,

733
00:45:07,199 --> 00:45:08,460
[SPEAKER_00] po nastanku,

734
00:45:08,460 --> 00:45:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] nama najbliža.

735
00:45:09,559 --> 00:45:11,460
[SPEAKER_00] To je najmlađa,

736
00:45:11,460 --> 00:45:11,699
[SPEAKER_00] dakle,

737
00:45:11,699 --> 00:45:13,280
[SPEAKER_00] najkasnije napisana

738
00:45:13,280 --> 00:45:14,460
[SPEAKER_00] knjiga staroga zavijeta.

739
00:45:14,460 --> 00:45:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ona nam najviše pomaže

740
00:45:16,159 --> 00:45:16,840
[SPEAKER_00] da shvatimo,

741
00:45:16,840 --> 00:45:17,119
[SPEAKER_00] prvo,

742
00:45:17,119 --> 00:45:17,980
[SPEAKER_00] da je tamo opisano

743
00:45:17,980 --> 00:45:18,800
[SPEAKER_00] ono što poznamo

744
00:45:18,800 --> 00:45:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] kao Isusovu sudbinu

745
00:45:19,960 --> 00:45:21,400
[SPEAKER_00] i da je to smješteno

746
00:45:21,400 --> 00:45:24,780
[SPEAKER_00] na iskustvo staroga zavijeta.

747
00:45:24,780 --> 00:45:25,599
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da,

748
00:45:25,599 --> 00:45:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] to su dva konkretna savjeta.

749
00:45:28,239 --> 00:45:30,380
[SPEAKER_00] Kako krenuti u studiji Biblije?

750
00:45:30,380 --> 00:45:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mislim da je nužno,

751
00:45:32,500 --> 00:45:34,360
[SPEAKER_00] sad ja moram sebe prisiliti

752
00:45:34,360 --> 00:45:36,159
[SPEAKER_00] pa pročitati sve od početka do kraja.

753
00:45:36,159 --> 00:45:37,719
[SPEAKER_00] To ljudi rade

754
00:45:37,719 --> 00:45:38,579
[SPEAKER_00] i to je u redu.

755
00:45:38,579 --> 00:45:40,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ja ne mislim da je to

756
00:45:40,179 --> 00:45:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji način,

757
00:45:43,179 --> 00:45:44,239
[SPEAKER_00] nego radi ovo.

758
00:45:44,239 --> 00:45:46,139
[SPEAKER_00] Uzmite si jedno evanđelje

759
00:45:46,139 --> 00:45:48,079
[SPEAKER_00] koje vas iz bilo kojeg razloga

760
00:45:48,079 --> 00:45:49,260
[SPEAKER_00] privlači poznajte ga

761
00:45:49,260 --> 00:45:50,940
[SPEAKER_00] i obuhvatite ga u cijelini.

762
00:45:50,940 --> 00:45:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] A kad ste to napravili,

763
00:45:52,500 --> 00:45:53,519
[SPEAKER_00] onda priđite na sljedeće.

764
00:45:53,519 --> 00:45:55,239
[SPEAKER_00] E, a za stari zavijet

765
00:45:55,239 --> 00:45:57,780
[SPEAKER_00] prostudirajte knjigu mudrosti.

766
00:45:57,780 --> 00:45:58,820
[SPEAKER_00] Pa onda krenite

767
00:45:58,820 --> 00:45:59,659
[SPEAKER_00] odakle hoćete.

768
00:45:59,659 --> 00:46:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] E, i onda isto,

769
00:46:01,119 --> 00:46:02,840
[SPEAKER_00] ovo, baš iz današnjih ispita,

770
00:46:02,840 --> 00:46:04,920
[SPEAKER_00] što je najvrijednije.

771
00:46:04,920 --> 00:46:06,539
[SPEAKER_00] Ne, ne mučit se sad,

772
00:46:06,539 --> 00:46:08,360
[SPEAKER_00] ja moram to redom sve čitat,

773
00:46:08,360 --> 00:46:09,500
[SPEAKER_00] što je u redu,

774
00:46:09,500 --> 00:46:13,679
[SPEAKER_00] nego pratiti ono što me interesira,

775
00:46:13,679 --> 00:46:14,679
[SPEAKER_00] recimo,

776
00:46:14,679 --> 00:46:15,900
[SPEAKER_00] to je najbolje.

777
00:46:15,900 --> 00:46:18,559
[SPEAKER_00] Što se čita u dnevnim čitanja?

778
00:46:18,559 --> 00:46:20,260
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da malo vidim što je to.

779
00:46:20,260 --> 00:46:21,739
[SPEAKER_00] Recimo, sad opet slušamo

780
00:46:21,739 --> 00:46:23,179
[SPEAKER_00] povijest Abrahamovu.

781
00:46:23,179 --> 00:46:24,440
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da je vidim u cijelini

782
00:46:24,440 --> 00:46:25,659
[SPEAKER_00] Abrahamovu povijest.

783
00:46:25,659 --> 00:46:27,460
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, to mislim da je puno bolje

784
00:46:27,460 --> 00:46:29,239
[SPEAKER_00] i to je zahtjevno,

785
00:46:29,239 --> 00:46:31,519
[SPEAKER_00] jer onda mi paralelno više stvari studiramo.

786
00:46:31,519 --> 00:46:33,760
[SPEAKER_00] U Svetom pismo redovito imamo,

787
00:46:33,760 --> 00:46:36,500
[SPEAKER_00] ne, u misnim čitanjima redovito

788
00:46:36,500 --> 00:46:38,780
[SPEAKER_00] imamo dva ili tri čitanja,

789
00:46:38,900 --> 00:46:40,519
[SPEAKER_00] ili još psalam, to je četvrto.

790
00:46:40,519 --> 00:46:43,179
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to je paralelno studiran više djelova

791
00:46:43,179 --> 00:46:44,199
[SPEAKER_00] Svetog pisma.

792
00:46:44,199 --> 00:46:45,059
[SPEAKER_00] To je napornije,

793
00:46:45,059 --> 00:46:46,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali je plodnije.

794
00:46:46,420 --> 00:46:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] Nakon jedne godine

795
00:46:47,880 --> 00:46:50,519
[SPEAKER_00] ja imam uvid u cijelo Sveto pismo.

796
00:46:50,519 --> 00:46:51,900
[SPEAKER_00] A inače, ovo je zgodno.

797
00:46:53,860 --> 00:46:58,500
[SPEAKER_00] Uskrsno vrijeme je korizma za stari zavjet.

798
00:46:58,500 --> 00:47:01,760
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to svi vjerojatno već je donekle i poznato.

799
00:47:01,760 --> 00:47:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] Mi redovito u liturgijskoj godini čitamo,

800
00:47:04,559 --> 00:47:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] eto, jedno čitanje je starozavjetno,

801
00:47:07,019 --> 00:47:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] jedno je novozavjetno.

802
00:47:07,940 --> 00:47:09,260
[SPEAKER_00] Osim u uskrsnom vremenu.

803
00:47:09,260 --> 00:47:12,139
[SPEAKER_00] U uskrsnom vremenu nema starozavjetnih čitanja,

804
00:47:12,139 --> 00:47:14,920
[SPEAKER_00] nego je obično dijela apostolska i poslanice.

805
00:47:14,920 --> 00:47:17,380
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, nema ovaj staroga zavjeta,

806
00:47:17,380 --> 00:47:19,699
[SPEAKER_00] pa se onda tako kaže šaljivo,

807
00:47:19,699 --> 00:47:22,179
[SPEAKER_00] jer to je post, to je korizma za stari zavjet.

808
00:47:22,179 --> 00:47:26,360
[SPEAKER_01] I imate svoj najdraži dio Svetog pisma.

809
00:47:26,360 --> 00:47:30,960
[SPEAKER_00] Uh, kad bi trebao jednu stvar istaknuti,

810
00:47:30,960 --> 00:47:34,559
[SPEAKER_00] onda moram reći da nekako ne postoji nešto

811
00:47:34,559 --> 00:47:38,099
[SPEAKER_00] što bih stalno isticao kao jednu moju stvar,

812
00:47:38,099 --> 00:47:41,159
[SPEAKER_00] ali znam da je bilo razdoblja kad sam bio poznat po tome,

813
00:47:41,159 --> 00:47:42,619
[SPEAKER_00] da sam stalno ponavljao,

814
00:47:42,619 --> 00:47:45,280
[SPEAKER_00] tješite, tješite narod moj.

815
00:47:45,280 --> 00:47:48,260
[SPEAKER_00] I to je i ozbiljno, nije to bilo samo nekakva šala,

816
00:47:48,260 --> 00:47:51,579
[SPEAKER_00] nego to je bilo doista nešto što je to početak

817
00:47:51,579 --> 00:47:53,920
[SPEAKER_00] drugog dijela Izaijine knjige,

818
00:47:53,920 --> 00:47:55,980
[SPEAKER_00] takozvani Deutero Izaija,

819
00:47:55,980 --> 00:47:57,039
[SPEAKER_00] gdje stvarno piša, jeli,

820
00:47:57,039 --> 00:48:01,960
[SPEAKER_00] i to je Božiji poziv da se njegov narod tješimo.

821
00:48:01,960 --> 00:48:05,679
[SPEAKER_00] Ono po čemu sam vjerojatno poznat

822
00:48:05,679 --> 00:48:08,260
[SPEAKER_00] kod onih koji me izliže ga znaju,

823
00:48:08,260 --> 00:48:10,539
[SPEAKER_00] je kao nekakav vrhunac

824
00:48:10,539 --> 00:48:14,780
[SPEAKER_00] cijelog svijetog pisma i zapravo ono što ono je reći,

825
00:48:14,780 --> 00:48:17,159
[SPEAKER_00] jedina Isusova nova zapovjed.

826
00:48:17,159 --> 00:48:19,920
[SPEAKER_00] Sam Isus kaže, sam gospodin kaže, to je nova zapovjed.

827
00:48:19,920 --> 00:48:23,059
[SPEAKER_00] Što će reći manje više ono ostalo,

828
00:48:23,059 --> 00:48:24,880
[SPEAKER_00] sve što gospodin daje,

829
00:48:24,880 --> 00:48:27,880
[SPEAKER_00] to je zapravo vraćanje na izvore,

830
00:48:28,000 --> 00:48:30,360
[SPEAKER_00] otkrivanje pravog značenja,

831
00:48:30,360 --> 00:48:32,360
[SPEAKER_00] onoga što je već u starom zavijetu,

832
00:48:32,360 --> 00:48:34,659
[SPEAKER_00] ili pravi smisa o zapovjedi Božih,

833
00:48:34,659 --> 00:48:35,539
[SPEAKER_00] a jedna je nova,

834
00:48:35,539 --> 00:48:37,300
[SPEAKER_00] i sigurno je, znate na pamet,

835
00:48:37,300 --> 00:48:39,980
[SPEAKER_00] ljubite jedni druge

836
00:48:39,980 --> 00:48:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] kao što sam ja vas ljubio.

837
00:48:42,719 --> 00:48:44,159
[SPEAKER_00] Pa u starom zavijetu

838
00:48:44,159 --> 00:48:45,420
[SPEAKER_00] veći imamo ljubi bližnjega,

839
00:48:45,420 --> 00:48:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] kao sebe samog.

840
00:48:46,440 --> 00:48:47,960
[SPEAKER_00] E, ali vidimo da je bitna novost,

841
00:48:47,960 --> 00:48:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] jeli, dakle, to više nije

842
00:48:49,280 --> 00:48:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] ljubi bližnjega u jednini,

843
00:48:51,440 --> 00:48:52,820
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, ti ljubiš,

844
