01:30:20,979 --> 01:30:23,119
[SPEAKER_00] u tebi mi s vami lina.

2028
01:30:23,119 --> 01:30:24,920
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, otac nebeski

2029
01:30:24,920 --> 01:30:25,720
[SPEAKER_00] koji proglašava,

2030
01:30:25,720 --> 01:30:27,819
[SPEAKER_00] to je bitni dio kršćanstva,

2031
01:30:27,819 --> 01:30:30,399
[SPEAKER_00] nije samo uzmi svoj križ,

2032
01:30:30,399 --> 01:30:31,520
[SPEAKER_00] nego biti s Isusom

2033
01:30:31,520 --> 01:30:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] onda kada otac nebeski proglašava

2034
01:30:33,800 --> 01:30:35,699
[SPEAKER_00] ti si moj, ja te volim,

2035
01:30:36,140 --> 01:30:37,500
[SPEAKER_00] ti si moja radost.

2036
01:30:37,500 --> 01:30:39,420
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, to bi bio taj vrhunac

2037
01:30:39,420 --> 01:30:41,060
[SPEAKER_00] koji se onda vjerojatno

2038
01:30:41,060 --> 01:30:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] u evanđeljima najviše prepoznaje

2039
01:30:43,859 --> 01:30:46,039
[SPEAKER_00] kada gospodin Isus uskrsli dolazi,

2040
01:30:46,039 --> 01:30:47,300
[SPEAKER_00] tada je mješavina,

2041
01:30:47,300 --> 01:30:49,520
[SPEAKER_00] ali u njima se rađa silna radost

2042
01:30:49,520 --> 01:30:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] i oni od radosti ne mogu vjerovati.

2043
01:30:51,920 --> 01:30:53,319
[SPEAKER_00] To je jedan trenutak

2044
01:30:53,319 --> 01:30:55,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji pokazuje o čemu je zapravo riječ.

2045
01:30:55,340 --> 01:30:57,500
[SPEAKER_01] Pater, kako vi objašnjate

2046
01:30:57,500 --> 01:30:59,020
[SPEAKER_01] knjigu otkrivenja?

2047
01:30:59,020 --> 01:31:02,640
[SPEAKER_01] Odnosno, kako ste ju vi prihvatili?

2048
01:31:02,640 --> 01:31:04,060
[SPEAKER_00] Razumijem pitanje.

2049
01:31:04,060 --> 01:31:05,079
[SPEAKER_00] Ja je ne objašnjam,

2050
01:31:05,079 --> 01:31:07,199
[SPEAKER_00] ja je pokušan čitat i razumijet.

2051
01:31:08,359 --> 01:31:10,100
[SPEAKER_00] dajmo sad malo reklamu.

2052
01:31:10,100 --> 01:31:13,060
[SPEAKER_00] Otiđite na YouTube,

2053
01:31:13,060 --> 01:31:14,779
[SPEAKER_00] pronađite kanal,

2054
01:31:14,779 --> 01:31:16,439
[SPEAKER_00] Hrvatski biblijski,

2055
01:31:16,439 --> 01:31:18,439
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno, ja, Hrvatski biblijski portal se zove.

2056
01:31:18,439 --> 01:31:20,979
[SPEAKER_00] I tamo pronađite cijelo tumačenje,

2057
01:31:20,979 --> 01:31:21,699
[SPEAKER_00] jedna emisija,

2058
01:31:21,699 --> 01:31:22,239
[SPEAKER_00] jedna emisija,

2059
01:31:22,239 --> 01:31:23,420
[SPEAKER_00] to je bilo, ja bih rekao,

2060
01:31:23,420 --> 01:31:25,460
[SPEAKER_00] uspješan razgovor o otkrivenju.

2061
01:31:27,340 --> 01:31:30,359
[SPEAKER_00] prvi odgovor je kako shvatiti knjigu otkrivenja,

2062
01:31:30,359 --> 01:31:31,720
[SPEAKER_00] uzmi i čitaj.

2063
01:31:31,720 --> 01:31:34,399
[SPEAKER_00] To je prvi odgovor za sve biblijske knjige.

2064
01:31:34,399 --> 01:31:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] Sasvim konkretno, vrlo je jednostavno.

2065
01:31:37,420 --> 01:31:43,520
[SPEAKER_00] Cijela knjiga otkrivenja uvijek govori o cijeloj povijesti Božjega naroda,

2066
01:31:43,880 --> 01:31:46,380
[SPEAKER_00] u više navrata se vraća na zemaljsku povijest,

2067
01:31:46,380 --> 01:31:49,199
[SPEAKER_00] a na početku i nakraj ima pogled na nebo.

2068
01:31:49,199 --> 01:31:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] Nebeskoj, nebeska crkva,

2069
01:31:51,260 --> 01:31:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] nebeski proslavljeni Božji svijet

2070
01:31:53,380 --> 01:31:55,260
[SPEAKER_00] i onda kako mi prolazimo

2071
01:31:55,260 --> 01:31:56,260
[SPEAKER_00] kroz cijelu povijest,

2072
01:31:56,260 --> 01:31:58,020
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo neki konkretni odlomare,

2073
01:31:58,020 --> 01:32:00,060
[SPEAKER_00] kako se uvijek uzima cijelina povijesti

2074
01:32:00,060 --> 01:32:02,100
[SPEAKER_00] i zanimljivo da je završetak

2075
01:32:02,100 --> 01:32:03,439
[SPEAKER_00] da nebeski Jeruzalem

2076
01:32:03,439 --> 01:32:05,140
[SPEAKER_00] dolazi na zemlju,

2077
01:32:05,140 --> 01:32:07,239
[SPEAKER_00] spušta se, dakle to je bit

2078
01:32:07,239 --> 01:32:09,319
[SPEAKER_00] kršćanstva, je da je gospodin Isus došao

2079
01:32:09,319 --> 01:32:11,039
[SPEAKER_00] na ovaj naš svijet, naša povijest

2080
01:32:11,039 --> 01:32:13,920
[SPEAKER_00] je obilježena jaganjcem Božijem.

2081
01:32:13,920 --> 01:32:15,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, Isus je prije svega

2082
01:32:15,159 --> 01:32:16,899
[SPEAKER_00] jaganjac Božiju u otkrivenju

2083
01:32:16,899 --> 01:32:20,340
[SPEAKER_00] i to zaklani jaganjac Božiju.

2084
01:32:20,340 --> 01:32:22,899
[SPEAKER_00] I On je, On je pobjednik

2085
01:32:22,899 --> 01:32:24,020
[SPEAKER_00] nad zlom zvijeri.

2086
01:32:24,020 --> 01:32:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] Gdje se mi upuštamo previše

2087
01:32:25,739 --> 01:32:27,279
[SPEAKER_00] u to da ćemo mi to svojim snagama,

2088
01:32:27,279 --> 01:32:29,159
[SPEAKER_00] neće to baš biti dobro,

2089
01:32:29,159 --> 01:32:30,680
[SPEAKER_00] a On je pobjednik.

2090
01:32:30,680 --> 01:32:32,979
[SPEAKER_01] Patrš, to biste preporučili

2091
01:32:32,979 --> 01:32:34,560
[SPEAKER_01] nekome ko bi htio svaki dan

2092
01:32:34,560 --> 01:32:35,960
[SPEAKER_01] provoditi vrijeme s Bogom,

2093
01:32:35,960 --> 01:32:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] a možda nekoj stvari dati prednost.

2094
01:32:38,539 --> 01:32:39,560
[SPEAKER_01] Da li biste rekli,

2095
01:32:39,560 --> 01:32:40,899
[SPEAKER_01] idi svaki dan na misu,

2096
01:32:41,039 --> 01:32:42,140
[SPEAKER_01] to će ti biti punina.

2097
01:32:42,140 --> 01:32:43,840
[SPEAKER_01] Čite svaki dan sveto pismo,

2098
01:32:43,840 --> 01:32:45,659
[SPEAKER_01] u tome ćeš pronaći odgovore,

2099
01:32:45,659 --> 01:32:47,060
[SPEAKER_01] a nedjelja je dovoljna,

2100
01:32:47,060 --> 01:32:48,600
[SPEAKER_01] pjevaj psalme,

2101
01:32:48,600 --> 01:32:49,659
[SPEAKER_01] što bi bilo...

2102
01:32:49,659 --> 01:32:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] Draga Lidija,

2103
01:32:50,760 --> 01:32:53,060
[SPEAKER_00] koji je vaš odgovor na to pitanje?

2104
01:32:53,060 --> 01:32:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pa moglo bi biti i jedno i drugo.

2105
01:32:56,039 --> 01:32:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] Ok, ali mislim da ćemo se lako složiti.

2106
01:32:58,159 --> 01:33:01,000
[SPEAKER_00] Opće nije sporno i zapravo pitanje je vrlo jednostavno.

2107
01:33:01,000 --> 01:33:04,819
[SPEAKER_00] Središte i vrhunac kršćanskog života je sveta misa.

2108
01:33:04,819 --> 01:33:06,460
[SPEAKER_00] I iz prakse znam,

2109
01:33:06,460 --> 01:33:07,460
[SPEAKER_00] dakle, hvala Bogu,

2110
01:33:07,460 --> 01:33:10,659
[SPEAKER_00] da ljudi koji žele njegovati dnevni duhovni život,

2111
01:33:11,380 --> 01:33:13,020
[SPEAKER_00] a imaju ograničeno vrijeme,

2112
01:33:13,020 --> 01:33:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] jako su ispunjeni,

2113
01:33:15,800 --> 01:33:17,779
[SPEAKER_00] onda oni idu na misu.

2114
01:33:17,779 --> 01:33:18,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ona odi na misu

2115
01:33:18,840 --> 01:33:19,779
[SPEAKER_00] i onda im ja kažem,

2116
01:33:19,779 --> 01:33:22,619
[SPEAKER_00] evo, kad se ljudi muče,

2117
01:33:22,619 --> 01:33:24,359
[SPEAKER_00] ne mogu si naći remena za molitvom,

2118
01:33:24,359 --> 01:33:25,699
[SPEAKER_00] onda se slažemo oko toga,

2119
01:33:25,699 --> 01:33:27,859
[SPEAKER_00] pa ostanite nakon svete misa.

2120
01:33:27,859 --> 01:33:29,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ili dođete malo prije svete misa.

2121
01:33:29,800 --> 01:33:31,600
[SPEAKER_00] Zapravo bi bilo bolje nakon svete misa.

2122
01:33:31,600 --> 01:33:33,699
[SPEAKER_00] Ali definitivno, odgovor je vrlo jednostavan.

2123
01:33:33,699 --> 01:33:37,420
[SPEAKER_00] Sveta misa je vrhuna

2124
01:33:37,420 --> 01:33:39,000
[SPEAKER_00] i to je nešto isusovački,

2125
01:33:39,000 --> 01:33:39,600
[SPEAKER_00] treba reći.

2126
01:33:39,600 --> 01:33:40,819
[SPEAKER_00] To je isusovački.

2127
01:33:41,380 --> 01:33:44,760
[SPEAKER_00] Sveta misa je vrhunac naše molitve,

2128
01:33:44,760 --> 01:33:47,539
[SPEAKER_00] zato što nas čak i ne našam snagom.

2129
01:33:47,539 --> 01:33:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] Mi smo tu.

2130
01:33:48,119 --> 01:33:50,840
[SPEAKER_00] I to je jako važno i kao olakšanje.

2131
01:33:50,840 --> 01:33:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] Joj, bio sam rastresen,

2132
01:33:52,880 --> 01:33:53,500
[SPEAKER_00] mislao sam drugo.

2133
01:33:53,500 --> 01:33:55,079
[SPEAKER_00] U redu, ali ti si došao,

2134
01:33:55,079 --> 01:33:58,100
[SPEAKER_00] ti si fizički, ti si realno kao čovjek bio na misi.

2135
01:33:58,100 --> 01:34:00,720
[SPEAKER_00] A daj malo sad i gospodinu da čini svoje,

2136
01:34:00,720 --> 01:34:02,720
[SPEAKER_00] jer gospodin nas prima.

2137
01:34:02,720 --> 01:34:05,760
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam li ja sada u punom svijesti,

2138
01:34:05,760 --> 01:34:08,279
[SPEAKER_00] punom zanosu ili nisam po svoje slabosti,

2139
01:34:08,279 --> 01:34:10,260
[SPEAKER_00] ali gospodin nas prima

2140
01:34:10,260 --> 01:34:12,359
[SPEAKER_00] svoju žrtvu, svoj prinos Otcu.

2141
01:34:12,359 --> 01:34:13,579
[SPEAKER_00] A to je vrhunska molitva.

2142
01:34:13,579 --> 01:34:15,920
[SPEAKER_00] Opet se vraćamo na ono izvorno značenje žrtve,

2143
01:34:15,920 --> 01:34:17,880
[SPEAKER_00] koja nije oduzimanje života,

2144
01:34:17,880 --> 01:34:19,899
[SPEAKER_00] nego je prinošenje Otcu.

2145
01:34:19,899 --> 01:34:21,920
[SPEAKER_00] A u praksi to onda znači,

2146
01:34:21,920 --> 01:34:23,020
[SPEAKER_00] što je i predviđeno,

2147
01:34:23,020 --> 01:34:24,760
[SPEAKER_00] da nakon svete pričesti,

2148
01:34:24,760 --> 01:34:25,960
[SPEAKER_00] pa onda i nakon svete mise,

2149
01:34:25,960 --> 01:34:28,239
[SPEAKER_00] mogu, koliko god mi je moguće,

2150
01:34:28,239 --> 01:34:30,220
[SPEAKER_00] zadržati se u osobnom,

2151
01:34:30,380 --> 01:34:33,239
[SPEAKER_00] tihom, klanjanju, razgovoru s Isusom,

2152
01:34:33,239 --> 01:34:35,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji se htio sjediniti sa onom.

2153
01:34:35,739 --> 01:34:37,659
[SPEAKER_00] To je definitivno vrh.

2154
01:34:37,659 --> 01:34:40,159
[SPEAKER_00] A da kako da je u to uključeno svetopismo,

2155
01:34:40,159 --> 01:34:43,979
[SPEAKER_00] jer svaka sveta misa ima čitanja.

2156
01:34:43,979 --> 01:34:45,399
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kako smo rekli,

2157
01:34:45,399 --> 01:34:49,880
[SPEAKER_00] postoji vrijeme posta za stari zavijet,

2158
01:34:50,000 --> 01:34:51,060
[SPEAKER_00] jeste uskrsno vrijeme,

2159
01:34:51,060 --> 01:34:52,380
[SPEAKER_00] iz opravdanih razloga,

2160
01:34:52,380 --> 01:34:54,199
[SPEAKER_00] a u cijeloj cerkvenoj godini

2161
01:34:54,199 --> 01:34:56,340
[SPEAKER_00] mi čitamo i stari i novi savijet.

2162
01:34:56,340 --> 01:35:00,680
[SPEAKER_01] Pater, imate li neke planove za budućnost,

2163
01:35:00,680 --> 01:35:02,720
[SPEAKER_01] neki novi projekt koji planirate,

2164
01:35:02,720 --> 01:35:04,460
[SPEAKER_01] nešto novo,

2165
01:35:04,460 --> 01:35:05,979
[SPEAKER_01] čemu se usmiravate,

2166
01:35:05,979 --> 01:35:08,720
[SPEAKER_01] što proučavate,

2167
01:35:08,720 --> 01:35:12,560
[SPEAKER_00] instrument koji ćete svirati?

2168
01:35:12,560 --> 01:35:15,720
[SPEAKER_00] Želim koliko god je moguće

2169
01:35:15,720 --> 01:35:19,340
[SPEAKER_00] spremiti dobro predavanja

2170
01:35:19,340 --> 01:35:21,279
[SPEAKER_00] iz Svetoga pisma.

2171
01:35:21,279 --> 01:35:23,979
[SPEAKER_00] Već mi je tajnica donijela raspored

2172
01:35:23,979 --> 01:35:26,859
[SPEAKER_00] predviđeni za jeduću godinu.

2173
01:35:26,859 --> 01:35:29,520
[SPEAKER_00] Želim iskreno

2174
01:35:29,520 --> 01:35:32,319
[SPEAKER_00] u našoj dragoj palmi

2175
01:35:32,319 --> 01:35:35,960
[SPEAKER_00] svima onima koji dolaze,

2176
01:35:35,960 --> 01:35:37,640
[SPEAKER_00] tamo dolaze ljudi svaki dan,

2177
01:35:37,640 --> 01:35:40,680
[SPEAKER_00] omogućiti bilo slavljenje Svete mise,

2178
01:35:40,680 --> 01:35:42,460
[SPEAKER_00] bilo je u nekakvom propovjedi,

2179
01:35:42,460 --> 01:35:43,380
[SPEAKER_00] kad je predviđena,

2180
01:35:43,380 --> 01:35:46,119
[SPEAKER_00] koliko god je moguće dati ono

2181
01:35:46,119 --> 01:35:47,819
[SPEAKER_00] s čime sam onda ja zadovoljan.

2182
01:35:48,680 --> 01:35:50,619
[SPEAKER_00] u tom smislu da im ono osjeća,

2183
01:35:50,619 --> 01:35:53,140
[SPEAKER_00] evo, sada se dragi bog smiješka,

2184
01:35:53,140 --> 01:35:54,779
[SPEAKER_00] jer kad sam ja zadovoljan,

2185
01:35:54,779 --> 01:35:56,779
[SPEAKER_00] onda mislim da sam nekako najviše dao,

2186
01:35:56,779 --> 01:36:00,220
[SPEAKER_00] da su ljudi najviše mogli uzeti ono što njima koristi.

2187
01:36:00,220 --> 01:36:06,939
[SPEAKER_00] Želim da najesen se dogodi ono što zapravo najviše opet

2188
01:36:06,939 --> 01:36:08,640
[SPEAKER_00] naša majka Lenka,

2189
01:36:08,640 --> 01:36:09,819
[SPEAKER_00] gospođa Lenka Grčić,

2190
01:36:09,819 --> 01:36:10,640
[SPEAKER_00] voditeljica,

2191
01:36:10,640 --> 01:36:11,539
[SPEAKER_00] ureda, zaklade,

2192
01:36:11,539 --> 01:36:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] već organizira

2193
01:36:12,420 --> 01:36:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] sa, smijem tako reći,

2194
01:36:14,699 --> 01:36:16,380
[SPEAKER_00] svemogućim ovaj patrom,

2195
01:36:16,380 --> 01:36:17,399
[SPEAKER_00] tvrtkom barunom,

2196
01:36:17,399 --> 01:36:20,420
[SPEAKER_00] koji je vrhunski organizator.

2197
01:36:20,420 --> 01:36:23,880
[SPEAKER_00] Sprema se opet večer slavljenja

2198
01:36:23,880 --> 01:36:26,119
[SPEAKER_00] konceptnog oblika.

2199
01:36:27,920 --> 01:36:32,239
[SPEAKER_00] Prošli put je to bilo u Gospinu vrtu

2200
01:36:32,239 --> 01:36:33,979
[SPEAKER_00] ili u Gospinom parku na Stenjevcu

2201
01:36:33,979 --> 01:36:36,600
[SPEAKER_00] i glavni lik je bio naš omiljeni,

2202
01:36:36,600 --> 01:36:39,239
[SPEAKER_00] već i, hvala Bogu, proslavljeni Alan Hržica.

2203
01:36:39,239 --> 01:36:41,960
[SPEAKER_00] Sada već postoje neki planovi,

2204
01:36:41,960 --> 01:36:43,859
[SPEAKER_00] valjda smijem toliko reći,

2205
01:36:43,859 --> 01:36:44,819
[SPEAKER_00] nije to još potređeno,

2206
01:36:44,819 --> 01:36:46,979
[SPEAKER_00] ali po svoji prilici će to biti

2207
01:36:46,979 --> 01:36:48,819
[SPEAKER_00] na samom Jordanovcu,

2208
01:36:48,819 --> 01:36:51,920
[SPEAKER_00] gdje postoji ovaj mali Isusovački grad,

2209
01:36:51,920 --> 01:36:54,500
[SPEAKER_00] dakle stari kolegi kao stara zgrada.

2210
01:36:54,500 --> 01:36:56,279
[SPEAKER_00] Onda je to zgrada crkve,

2211
01:36:56,279 --> 01:36:57,460
[SPEAKER_00] onda zgrada fakulteta,

2212
01:36:57,640 --> 01:36:58,300
[SPEAKER_00] zgrada biblioteke,

2213
01:36:58,300 --> 01:37:00,020
[SPEAKER_00] slutim, da mi nisam to ja,

2214
01:37:00,020 --> 01:37:01,119
[SPEAKER_00] to su glazbenici rekli,

2215
01:37:01,119 --> 01:37:02,020
[SPEAKER_00] i sam Alan Hržica,

2216
01:37:02,020 --> 01:37:03,859
[SPEAKER_00] ja mislim da bi to tamo bilo

2217
01:37:03,859 --> 01:37:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] jako dobro napraviti,

2218
01:37:05,199 --> 01:37:06,899
[SPEAKER_00] a prednost je imamo parking.

2219
01:37:06,899 --> 01:37:09,239
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, daj Bože,

2220
01:37:09,239 --> 01:37:10,359
[SPEAKER_00] i vjerojatno,

2221
01:37:10,359 --> 01:37:11,859
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno mislim da je već rekla

2222
01:37:11,859 --> 01:37:15,060
[SPEAKER_00] da naša mlada umjetnica,

2223
01:37:15,060 --> 01:37:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] gospođa Vanessa Mioč,

2224
01:37:16,539 --> 01:37:17,539
[SPEAKER_00] koja bi vjerojatno bila

2225
01:37:17,539 --> 01:37:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] glavni lik i tako,

2226
01:37:19,960 --> 01:37:22,380
[SPEAKER_00] evo to je da koliko god mogu

2227
01:37:22,380 --> 01:37:23,079
[SPEAKER_00] pomognemo,

2228
01:37:23,079 --> 01:37:25,079
[SPEAKER_00] podržimo u organizaciji.

2229
01:37:27,359 --> 01:37:30,279
[SPEAKER_00] moja osobna želja,

2230
01:37:30,279 --> 01:37:34,020
[SPEAKER_00] ili ono što smatram da me nekako mene veseli,

2231
01:37:34,020 --> 01:37:36,680
[SPEAKER_00] a valjda ima nekakav odjek

2232
01:37:36,680 --> 01:37:40,859
[SPEAKER_00] sa recimo sedamnaest tisuća pratitelja

2233
01:37:40,859 --> 01:37:42,439
[SPEAKER_00] ili sa na fejsu

2234
01:37:42,439 --> 01:37:46,079
[SPEAKER_00] i pet tisuća četiristo pratitelja

2235
01:37:46,079 --> 01:37:46,899
[SPEAKER_00] na YouTube-u,

2236
01:37:46,899 --> 01:37:48,979
[SPEAKER_00] i notabene,

2237
01:37:48,979 --> 01:37:51,100
[SPEAKER_00] velik dio prelazi

2238
01:37:51,100 --> 01:37:53,460
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj rub katoličke crkve,

2239
01:37:53,460 --> 01:37:55,239
[SPEAKER_00] dakle puno ih iz pravoslavlja,

2240
01:37:55,319 --> 01:37:56,159
[SPEAKER_00] koji to prate.

2241
01:37:56,159 --> 01:37:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] Moja želja da, evo,

2242
01:37:57,840 --> 01:38:00,199
[SPEAKER_00] nastajim dnevno evanđelje

2243
01:38:00,199 --> 01:38:02,739
[SPEAKER_00] pretočiti, zapravo molitveni tekst,

2244
01:38:02,739 --> 01:38:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] koji je, koliko je moguće,

2245
01:38:04,340 --> 01:38:05,180
[SPEAKER_00] aktualan.

2246
01:38:05,180 --> 01:38:09,020
[SPEAKER_00] To je meni jedno veliko obogaćenje,

2247
01:38:09,020 --> 01:38:11,260
[SPEAKER_00] koje onda na taj modern način dijelim

2248
01:38:11,260 --> 01:38:13,140
[SPEAKER_00] i čini se da ima nekog odjeka.

2249
01:38:13,979 --> 01:38:16,539
[SPEAKER_00] i ovo stvaranje tih salama,

2250
01:38:16,539 --> 01:38:18,319
[SPEAKER_00] koji su i za slušanje, za uporabu.

2251
01:38:18,319 --> 01:38:21,520
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, evo, nekih velikih projekata ne imam.

2252
01:38:21,520 --> 01:38:22,819
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam u svojoj zajednici,

2253
01:38:22,819 --> 01:38:24,119
[SPEAKER_00] evo, sad je već došao raspored

2254
01:38:24,119 --> 01:38:25,560
[SPEAKER_00] za ovaj iduću godinu,

2255
01:38:25,560 --> 01:38:27,420
[SPEAKER_00] Patria Provincijal svake godine

2256
01:38:27,420 --> 01:38:28,640
[SPEAKER_00] praktički određuje,

2257
01:38:28,640 --> 01:38:29,659
[SPEAKER_00] jel, ili potvrđuje.

2258
01:38:30,659 --> 01:38:33,039
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam, evo, kao duhovnik u zajednici

2259
01:38:33,039 --> 01:38:37,180
[SPEAKER_00] i zapravo to, taj posao jako, jako cijenim

2260
01:38:37,180 --> 01:38:41,039
[SPEAKER_00] i volim, dakle, biti nekakav voditelj

2261
01:38:41,039 --> 01:38:42,279
[SPEAKER_00] naših duhovnih točaka

2262
01:38:42,279 --> 01:38:44,739
[SPEAKER_00] i onda, eto, koliko god je moguće

2263
01:38:44,739 --> 01:38:48,840
[SPEAKER_00] biti na raspolaganju, dakle, patrima, subraći,

2264
01:38:48,840 --> 01:38:50,859
[SPEAKER_00] jel, da mogu, koliko je to,

2265
01:38:50,859 --> 01:38:52,340
[SPEAKER_00] evo, Bogu se želi sa nama poslušiti

2266
01:38:52,340 --> 01:38:53,640
[SPEAKER_00] da budem potporan njima

2267
01:38:53,640 --> 01:38:55,479
[SPEAKER_00] u njihovom duhovnom životu.

2268
01:38:55,479 --> 01:38:59,020
[SPEAKER_00] To smatram da sam posve nedostojan

2269
01:38:59,020 --> 01:39:00,420
[SPEAKER_00] i da sam nestručan

2270
01:39:00,420 --> 01:39:02,020
[SPEAKER_00] i da nisam sposoban, jel,

2271
01:39:02,020 --> 01:39:04,340
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno, da, dragi Bogu, svoja čuda čini,

2272
01:39:04,340 --> 01:39:06,859
[SPEAKER_00] ali to smatram vrhunskom, vrhunskom zadačom

2273
01:39:06,859 --> 01:39:08,680
[SPEAKER_00] i, dakle, najvećom čašću,

2274
01:39:08,680 --> 01:39:09,760
[SPEAKER_00] najvećim zdovoljstvom

2275
01:39:09,760 --> 01:39:11,399
[SPEAKER_00] i ako tu išta dobro učinim,

2276
01:39:11,399 --> 01:39:13,720
[SPEAKER_00] to smatram ostvarenjem svoje karijere.

2277
01:39:13,720 --> 01:39:16,859
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam puno, Patr.

2278
01:39:16,859 --> 01:39:19,859
[SPEAKER_01] Niko, hvala vam, evo, na ovom razgovoru,

2279
01:39:19,859 --> 01:39:23,680
[SPEAKER_01] na sudjelovanju u projektima i programima

2280
01:39:23,680 --> 01:39:25,319
[SPEAKER_01] naše udruge Hrvatska za život,

2281
01:39:25,319 --> 01:39:27,340
[SPEAKER_01] na pomoći, na uvijek,

2282
01:39:28,020 --> 01:39:31,680
[SPEAKER_01] velikoj vedrini radosti i mudrosti

2283
01:39:31,680 --> 01:39:33,300
[SPEAKER_01] koju nam donesete.

2284
01:39:33,300 --> 01:39:36,220
[SPEAKER_01] I evo, ko znao, možda ćete opet biti ovako

2285
01:39:36,220 --> 01:39:37,579
[SPEAKER_01] ispred naših kamera.

2286
01:39:37,579 --> 01:39:42,319
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, kamere su dio naših modernog života.

2287
01:39:42,319 --> 01:39:45,939
[SPEAKER_00] Naviko sam, početku sam ima velike probleme,

2288
01:39:45,939 --> 01:39:48,760
[SPEAKER_00] ali sam, međerom, puno toga već, evo, odradio

2289
01:39:48,760 --> 01:39:51,140
[SPEAKER_00] i to mi je jedan dragi dio posla.

2290
01:39:51,460 --> 01:39:54,920
[SPEAKER_00] baš pod ovim vidikom, jednom se iznese i onda stoji.

2291
01:39:54,920 --> 01:39:56,420
[SPEAKER_00] Na raspolaganju je doista,

2292
01:39:56,420 --> 01:39:59,020
[SPEAKER_00] mislim da je to i u znanosti jako važno.

2293
01:39:59,020 --> 01:40:01,020
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, dostupno je svima,

2294
01:40:01,020 --> 01:40:03,020
[SPEAKER_00] svakda, jel'i?

2295
01:40:03,020 --> 01:40:05,199
[SPEAKER_00] A sad, ako je neka knjiga, ako će i naći,

2296
01:40:05,199 --> 01:40:05,880
[SPEAKER_00] jel'i dok dođe do nje.

2297
01:40:05,880 --> 01:40:10,100
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, ja se veselim i zapravo bih htio završiti s ovim,

2298
01:40:10,100 --> 01:40:17,939
[SPEAKER_00] pa nisam ja počeo, ovaj, sorađivati sa vašim vrijednim pokretom

2299
01:40:17,939 --> 01:40:21,520
[SPEAKER_00] tako da sam, evo, ispovjednik i nekako pomoćnik

2300
01:40:21,520 --> 01:40:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] u ovom dubinskom radu, ovaj, vikendu,

2301
01:40:25,380 --> 01:40:28,279
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno duho one vježbe, oprostom oslobođene,

2302
01:40:28,279 --> 01:40:32,779
[SPEAKER_00] nego radosni trenuci gdje, valjda po rasporedu misnom,

2303
01:40:32,880 --> 01:40:37,819
[SPEAKER_00] sam baš bio zadržen svetom misu kad je procesija za život u Zagrebu,

2304
01:40:37,819 --> 01:40:42,020
[SPEAKER_00] jel'i koja, mislim, još uvijek kreće od majke Bože kam ih vratio,

2305
01:40:42,020 --> 01:40:43,100
[SPEAKER_00] a dolazi do bazilika.

2306
01:40:43,100 --> 01:40:45,840
[SPEAKER_00] I sad ja sam jednom, drugi, treći put, valjda bio,

2307
01:40:45,840 --> 01:40:49,060
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, i to je mene jednostavno tematski me jako oduševljava,

2308
01:40:49,060 --> 01:40:52,180
[SPEAKER_00] i onda sam naišao na takav odaziv, takvu radost,

2309
01:40:52,180 --> 01:40:54,960
[SPEAKER_00] pogotovo kad tamo dođu i djeca, jel'i to je uvijek od svete mise,

2310
01:40:54,960 --> 01:40:55,960
[SPEAKER_00] ovaj, nešto posebno.

2311
01:40:55,960 --> 01:40:59,840
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, pa se veselim pogotovo takvom svakom događaju,

2312
01:41:00,479 --> 01:41:03,939
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je to onda i javno, i privlači,

2313
01:41:03,939 --> 01:41:09,479
[SPEAKER_00] i to je posebno svjedočanstvo, jel'i kada vi dovedete cijelu svoju obitelj,

2314
01:41:09,479 --> 01:41:11,220
[SPEAKER_00] i to se pokaže u javnosti,

2315
01:41:11,220 --> 01:41:13,220
[SPEAKER_00] i to jednostavno samo, ne treba ništa govoriti,

2316
01:41:13,220 --> 01:41:15,779
[SPEAKER_00] to već odjekne, i to je poziv onda,

2317
01:41:15,779 --> 01:41:18,479
[SPEAKER_00] evo, doista da dođemo k Isusu.

2318
01:41:18,479 --> 01:41:20,020
[SPEAKER_00] Mi znamo da gospodin Isus kaže,

2319
01:41:20,640 --> 01:41:24,479
[SPEAKER_00] pustite malene k meni, to je prvi razlog zašto se isplati ima djecu,

2320
01:41:24,479 --> 01:41:27,260
[SPEAKER_00] a drugi razlog je vrlo konkretan,

2321
01:41:27,260 --> 01:41:30,520
[SPEAKER_00] kad se radi o tome ko je najveći i kako ući u kraljostvo Božje,

2322
01:41:30,520 --> 01:41:31,779
[SPEAKER_00] gospodin uzima dijete.

2323
01:41:31,779 --> 01:41:34,619
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, ako odustanemo od djece, onda smo gotovi,

2324
01:41:34,619 --> 01:41:36,920
[SPEAKER_00] nema nam kraljostva, nećemo ući u njega.

2325
01:41:37,340 --> 01:41:40,979
[SPEAKER_00] Evo, u tom smislu, želim reći hvala vama,

2326
01:41:40,979 --> 01:41:44,640
[SPEAKER_00] i svima onima, i u Hrvatskoj, i po cijelom svijetu,

2327
01:41:44,640 --> 01:41:49,119
[SPEAKER_00] koji se nesebično zalažu u ovom projektu,

2328
01:41:49,119 --> 01:41:51,100
[SPEAKER_00] koji je konkretna briga za budućnost.

2329
01:41:51,100 --> 01:41:52,880
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala vam puno, paterniko.

2330
01:41:52,880 --> 01:41:57,640
[SPEAKER_01] Dragi naši pratitelji YouTube kanala Udruga je Hrvatska za život,

2331
01:41:57,640 --> 01:42:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] bio je ovo još jedan podcast život.

2332
01:42:00,079 --> 01:42:02,439
[SPEAKER_01] Pratite nas i dalje. Hvala Isusi, Marija.

2333
01:42:07,340 --> 01:42:14,420
[UNKNOWN] Hvala Isusi, Marija.

